<header class="bg-gradient-to-b from-neutral-50 to-yellow-50">
  <div class="flex flex-col lg:flex-row">
    <div class="flex flex-col items-center lg:w-1/2">
      <span class="text-xl lg:text-2xl pt-20 text-center">Sun City Aviation Academy is Your</span>
      <h1 class="font-bold text-5xl pt-5 text-center">Pathway to the Airlines</h1>
      <h2 class="font-semibold text-lg italic pt-5 pb-10 text-center">We're here to help you achieve your aviation goals.  <br class="hidden lg:block">Every step of the way.</h2>
      <p class="w-3/4 pb-20">
        If you're new to the aviation world, you've likely encountered a bunch of online resources, leaving you more confused than when you started. How extensive is pilot training and what are the requirements? Are those smaller aircraft considered safe? We'll provide answers to these inquiries and more in the following sections.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="flex flex-col justify-center items-center lg:w-1/2">
      <%= image_tag "sun-city-inside-airliner.webp", alt: "Sun City team member and alumni inside airliner cockpit", class: "lg:w-3/4 rounded-xl"%>
    </div>
  </div>
</header>

<section class="bg-gradient-to-b from-neutral-500 to-neutral-900 flex flex-col items-center text-white">
  <div class="pt-10 flex flex-col items-center">
    <h2 class="text-center text-2xl lg:text-4xl font-bold">Determine if <span class="text-custom-50">Pilot Training</span> is Right For You</h2>
    <p class="w-3/4 lg:w-1/2  pt-10">Starting the journey to become a pilot is a big decision. First, think about what you want and how flying fits in. Do you want to fly for fun with friends and family, enjoy beautiful views, and visit nearby places? Or do you want a job as a pilot, like flying for an airline?</p>
    <p class="w-3/4 lg:w-1/2  py-10">Also, think about how much time you can spend on flight training and make sure your family and friends are okay with it. Before you begin pilot training, ask yourself these important questions. Remember, no matter your situation or dreams, the Sun City team is here to help you achieve your flying goals.</p>
    <%= link_to "TAKE OUR QUIZ", quiz_path, target: "blank", data: { turbo: false }, class: "btn-primary mb-10" %>
  </div>
</section>








<section class="bg-gradient-to-b from-slate-50 to-white flex flex-col lg:flex-row lg:items-start items-center pt-10 pb-0 lg:py-10">
  <div class="flex flex-col items-center justify-center lg:w-1/2 ">
    <h2 class="text-3xl font-semibold pb-10 font-sans mx-5 text-center">Pilots are Professionals</h2>
    <p class="w-3/4 pb-10">Regardless if you're flying a small plane or a big airliner, all pilots are professionals who fly and operate airplanes. They usually have certain qualities that help them do their job well.</p>
    <p class="w-3/4 pb-10">If you're excited about flying high or interested in becoming a pilot, please don't hesitate to reach out to us. Contact us today to start an exciting adventure in aviation.</p>
    <p class="w-3/4 pb-10 font-semibold font-sans">Reach out to the Sun City team, and together let's achieve your aviation dreams.</p>
    <%= link_to "CONTACT US", contact_path, data: { turbo: false }, class: "btn-primary mb-10" %>
  </div>
  <div class="flex flex-col items-center lg:w-1/2 pb-10 lg:pb-0">
    <h2 class="text-3xl font-semibold pb-10 font-sans mx-5 text-center">Are You a Pilot?</h2>
    <div class="flex flex-col w-3/4">
      <div class="flex flex-row flex-start">
        <div class="text-custom-50 pr-2 font-extrabold">✈</div>
        <h3 class="text-lg px-5 text-left">Professionalism and discipline</h3>
      </div>
      <div class="pl-11 italic text-slate-500">Pilots need to be professional all the time. They follow the rules, stick to procedures, and put passengers' safety and comfort first.</div>
      <div class="flex flex-row flex-start pt-3">
        <div class="text-custom-50 pr-2 font-extrabold">✈</div>
        <h3 class="text-lg px-5 text-left">Strong situational awareness</h3>
      </div>
      <div class="pl-11 italic text-slate-500">Pilots must know what's going on around them to make safe choices. They need to be good at understanding the weather, other planes, and their own aircraft.</div>
      <div class="flex flex-row flex-start pt-3">
        <div class="text-custom-50 pr-2 font-extrabold">✈</div>
        <h3 class="text-lg px-5 text-left">Cool under pressure</h3>
      </div>
      <div class="pl-11 italic text-slate-500">Pilots need to stay relaxed and collected when things get stressful. They have to stay focused and make smart decisions, even in difficult or emergency situations.</div>
      <div class="flex flex-row flex-start pt-3">
        <div class="text-custom-50 pr-2 font-extrabold">✈</div>
        <h3 class="text-lg px-5 text-left">Excellent at communication</h3>
      </div>
      <div class="pl-11 italic text-slate-500">Pilots need to communicate effectively. They have to share important information clearly and listen carefully to instructions and updates.</div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>



